The transliteration layer derives from community EVA transliterations
(Takeshi Takahashi; Zandbergen–Landini ZL3b for the Rosettes foldout) with
editorial corrections and reading order by A. Placa — credit those authors
when reusing the text layer. Manuscript images are not included.
